{"tid":1022613,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"比蝗蟲偷手機 去差館冇人幫","createTime":"2019-02-15T06:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T16:50:45.000Z","uid":70959,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9049a21c9b2d33e13da56ce3756386ca6dfb7151","tid":1022613,"uid":70959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"情人節嗰日漏咗手機喺巴士 <br />\n過咗幾個鐘時候先發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就用我朋友手機係咁打我個電話 <br />\n跟住就有一個電話打黎我朋友手機同我地講<br />\n佢執到我個手機咁我就問佢係邊想拎返部機<br />\n不過佢下下都唔講佢係邊 <br />\n已經覺得佢好撚可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打咗15次電話佢先聽一次<br />\n最後同我講係一個location等 屌佢老味等左成個鐘都唔見人仲要熄手機 屌佢個老母個閪仲要熄食埋我個手機 wtf<br />\n分明個蝗蟲喺度玩我....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尋晚去咗差局報案 不過啲差佬話幫唔到我.....<br />\n我已經打咗好多次電話比自己同個蝗蟲<br />\n唔知係咪俾佢block左....<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>個蝗蟲電話係5620 2230<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n我依家真係好無奈 希望各位好心人教我可以點<br />\n手機裏面太多回憶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚戇鳩嘅就係我唔見手機之前教咗去靜音同無turn on gps所以用find my device 都係冇用"},{"pid":"79c823b99dd1f2cd3229f978ff83502387f16704","tid":1022613,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"帶咗番大陸啦"},{"pid":"039b7b27781d6e37ae7ada8cd1b010b68b7f468d","tid":1022613,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:58:04.000Z","msg":"返左大陸點幫"},{"pid":"266ad1aa51aa7b7e27566cddb7b0ebaa06c7061e","tid":1022613,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"無開gps搵西咩"},{"pid":"e92722cc83d1200b4666848551a068a92934d67d","tid":1022613,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"包容下啦"},{"pid":"5ef6d80c92adc948f2894d91de6fbf7a6ef3ff6e","tid":1022613,"uid":155818,"like":0,"disli